Version 0.3.0
-------------

- Adds `can` method
- Drops Python 2.7 support
- Adds Python 3.8 support

Version 0.2.0
-------------

- Raises Forbidden (403) instead of Unauthorized (401)
- Drops Python 2.6 support

Version 0.1.13
--------------

- Adds init_app method
- More standard way of registering extensions
- Added AUTHORS file
- Added CHANGES file